WEBVTT

00:11:26.720 --> 00:11:30.736
Similarly, employment growth
is robust in many low-skill,

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:33.816
low-education jobs like food service,

00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:36.096
cleaning, security,

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:37.360
home health aids.

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:41.176
Simultaneously, employment is shrinking

00:11:41.200 --> 00:11:45.256
in many middle-education,
middle-wage, middle-class jobs,

00:11:45.280 --> 00:11:49.096
like blue-collar production
and operative positions

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:52.096
and white-collar
clerical and sales positions.

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:54.376
The reasons behind this contracting middle

00:11:54.400 --> 00:11:55.616
are not mysterious.

00:11:55.640 --> 00:11:57.616
Many of those middle-skill jobs

00:11:57.640 --> 00:12:00.136
use well-understood rules and procedures